data.description: NEW YEAR NEW PRICE!!  READY...SET..MOVE!!  SELLER OFFERING $4,000.00 Fence Credit with ACCEPTABLE offer!! Welcome to this well-maintained move in ready 4 bedroom, 2 bath home built in 2019 in the popular subdivision of Bridge Harbor. Just minutes to Tyndall AFB & Mexico Beach! This house has SOLAR  PANELS, a spacious main room, kitchen island, laundry room, and so much more! This sought-after subdivision offers a community pool, small tree shaded area for picnics or gatherings. A friendly welcoming atmosphere. Close to shopping, boat ramps, and scenic parks! Seller is MOTIVATED, bring us an OFFER!
